Source: jvgs
Section: games
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Joao Pinto <joao.pinto@getdeb.net>
Build-Depends: cdbs, debhelper (>= 7), cmake, swig,
 libsdl1.2-dev, libsdl-mixer1.2-dev, liblua5.1-0-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.1
Homepage: http://jvgs.sourceforge.net/

Package: jvgs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, jvgs-data (= ${source:Version})
Description: minimalistic platform game
 JVGS is an open source platform game that is not like the others.
 It is build on simple line structures loaded from svg files,
 giving the whole game a "sketched" and minimalistic look.
 Levels can be made with simple xml and lua files.

Package: jvgs-data
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: minimalistic platform game - data
 JVGS is an open source platform game that is not like the others.
 It is build on simple line structures loaded from svg files,
 giving the whole game a "sketched" and minimalistic look.
 Levels can be made with simple xml and lua files.
 .
 (This package contains the data files)
